Basic differece between array and arraylist is 
that array has a predefined number of elements whereas;
arraylist is a dynamic array

Dynamic array creates a array of double size when the
array is filledsome functions 
ArraysList<Datatype> arr = new ArraysList<>(Initial sizr)
arr.add(Index , value); to add a element
arr.get(index); to print an element 
arr.set(Index, value); to change the value
arr.add(value); to add element in the last
arr.remove(index); removes that index